    "answer": "$$\n\\begin{aligned}\n& \\operatorname{Pr}(X=1)={ }_n C_x \\cdot p^x \\cdot q^{n-x}={ }_4 C_1 \\cdot 0.75^1 \\cdot 0.25^{4-1}=4 \\cdot 0.75 \\cdot \\\n& 25=0.0469 .\n\\end{aligned}\n$$"
